// Correctness arc 5 (h) sibling: var decls DO range-check literal shapes
// (adapt_untyped_int_operand -> check_literal_range rejects
// `var v int8 = 300`) but a CONST IDENTIFIER is not a literal leaf, so
// `var v int8 = a` fell through to the any-int type_compatible and codegen
// truncated the store — this printed 44. The ident-bearing shapes now route
// through the shared fold-based core; PURE literal shapes deliberately keep
// the per-literal adapter semantics (including its documented `100 + 100`
// deviation) — no previously-accepted literal program changes behavior.
package main

func main() {
	const a = 300
	var v int8 = a
	println(v)
}
